{"tid":2089032,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人可唔可以團結一次","createTime":"2020-07-01T13:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T14:08:09.000Z","uid":161174,"like":21,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8fc90cfdb753d378bc928d520eb388a03c747daa","tid":2089032,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:00:15.000Z","msg":"呢刻要嘅已經唔喺上街<br />\n聽日如果都唔罷工罷課其實可以去食屎<br />\n都講過好多次場運動有前冇後<br />\n冇後退嘅機會，政權一但走向極權<br />\n係唔會返到轉頭，狗隻得到嘅權力越黎越大，政治部都成立埋<br />\n之前出文問過大家，冇豁出去爭取民主自由嘅心真係唔好搞咁多，每出一條惡法上街一次，有幾多人命前途可以燒<br />\n一國一制已經開始，上街表達意見都做唔到嘅呢刻，你準備抗爭還是繼續返工？<br />\n<br />\n轉自tg<br />\n借用一吓"},{"pid":"c859934a73636a61a229e20cd04b51d1e60b12c0","tid":2089032,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9d7a87f4f7f08a4af6f64bfabfc06235b7071a","tid":2089032,"uid":161174,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:06:08.000Z","msg":"我唔係想放負<br />\n但大家一齊團結一次<br />\n罷工罷課<br />\n令個社會停轉一日"},{"pid":"4f2afc483f36a76f8e7f95dda223ba5263b887a3","tid":2089032,"uid":188580,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:09:47.000Z","msg":"啱啱講完BNO平權啲人已經討論緊走<br />\n真係唔想最後一條防線都無埋-香港人嘅團結同信念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb3e5d2099fc7f4af97f9887eca414a8634978f","tid":2089032,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:10:41.000Z","msg":"1-5返工食黃店"},{"pid":"30703f91f78b1137f609b12df501dbdf1d1b015a","tid":2089032,"uid":268896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:10:50.000Z","msg":"立即無限期大三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b924c29dd355e6531fc5a449c7141ff9d1297ccb",